## ğŸ® Gameplay Overview

In BK Fight Game, two playersâ€”**Putin** and **Trump**â€”face off in a turn-based battle.

- Both fighters start with **100 health points**.
- Each player can attack the opponent using their dedicated **"Attack"** button.
